data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value: In this mode audio/video files can be stream copied, provided they share qualities (size, codec, bitrate). NOTE: Not all containers are supported for stream copy. If playback issues occur or files are not joined, re-encoding is required.

data.name: txt_batch_concat.Text
data.value: In this mode initial and/or end file will be concatenated to every file on the list, instead of concatenating all files together.
